FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FThe inquiry, chaired by Lord Turnbull,
OL,7,Fwas set up following a number of legal
OL,8,Fchallenges brought by campaigners, to
OL,9,Fexamine whether the explosion could
OL,10,Fhave been prevented by UK authorities.
OL,12,FOn Monday, the inquiry heard
OL,13,Fapplications on behalf of the PSNI in
OL,14,Frelation to anonymity for serving and
OL,15,Fformer police officers who may be
OL,16,Fcalled to give evidence.
OL,18,FLord Turnbull has previously granted
OL,19,Fan anonymity order for four retired
OL,20,Fofficers referred to as 1,2,3 and 5.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FIn doing so he requested the parties
OL,7,Fsubmit a "representative sample" of
OL,8,Fanonymity applications to establish
OL,9,F"issues of principle and fact" common
OL,10,Facross the cases.
OL,12,FMichael Mansfield KC, representing the
OL,13,Ffamily of Omagh victim Elizabeth Rush,
OL,14,Fsaid the submissions "should not be
OL,15,Fseen in isolation" given "what's about
OL,16,Fto come down the track which is in
OL,17,Ffact another set of not unrelated
OL,18,Fsubmissions concerned with closed
OL,19,Fmaterial".
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@`O]qD@AOUqD@^O]vD@VOUwD@RO]wD@
OL,26,AZOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,F"The family I represent are concerned
OL,7,Fin the longer run that we may have a
OL,8,Fsituation in which the families and
OL,9,Fthe public are not made aware, for
OL,10,Freasons to do with the restriction
OL,11,Forders, not only of the identity `
OL,12,Fthat's part of the situation ` but
OL,13,Fmore importantly of the substance of
OL,14,Factions that may have been taken by
OL,15,Fcertain individuals," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,F"And in the context of this inquiry,
OL,7,Fgiven the gravity of the original
OL,8,Foffence and also the repercussions
OL,9,Ffrom that, the need for accountability
OL,10,Fand truth at the same time ` that is
OL,11,Fone of the objectives we said was only
OL,12,Fobvious for the purpose of this
OL,13,Finquiry."
OL,15,FMr Mansfield said any potential
OL,16,F"preventability" of the attack is
OL,17,F"perhaps the core issue".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]xD@AOUxD@PO]yD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,F"We're concerned that preventability
OL,7,Fhinges in large measure upon one
OL,8,Fparticular factor, and that is
OL,9,Fintelligence and what was known and
OL,10,Fwhat wasn't known," he said.
OL,12,FHe added: "That's not to say undermine
OL,13,Fevery single application for that
OL,14,Freason, but there will be some in that
OL,15,Fnarrative that require public
OL,16,Faccountability.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,F"Otherwise, one would look back and
OL,7,Fwonder what has been the purpose of
OL,8,Fthe whole exercise if those matters
OL,9,Fare not canvassed and addressed in the
OL,10,Fspirit of transparency."
OL,12,FEarlier, Philip Henry KC representing
OL,13,Fthe PSNI outlined the police position
OL,14,Fof the ECHR Article 2 "test", meaning
OL,15,Fthey must show at the first stage a
OL,16,F"real and immediate risk to life" and
OL,17,Fat the second stage what is a
OL,18,F"proportionate measure" to be put in
OL,19,Fplace by the state arising from that
OL,20,Frisk.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]vD@WOUvD@\O]xD@AOUxD@aO]zD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FMr Henry said, from the material
OL,7,Fprovided to the inquiry, the stage 1
OL,8,Ftest of an immediate risk to life for
OL,9,Fformer officers giving evidence is
OL,10,F"satisfied", adding "we say that test
OL,11,Fis satisfied without reference to the
OL,12,Findividual circumstance of the retired
OL,13,Fofficers".
OL,15,FHe referred to a threat assessment
OL,16,Fprepared by the Joint Terrorism
OL,17,FAnalysis Centre (JTAC), a sub-unit
OL,18,Fwithin MI5.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]rD@UOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FIt highlights that the terrorist
OL,7,Fthreat level in Northern Ireland is
OL,8,Fdeemed substantial, meaning an attack
OL,9,Fis likely and dissident Republicans
OL,10,Fare assessed as "highly likely to view
OL,11,Fofficers and former officers as
OL,12,Flegitimate targets for any future
OL,13,Fattack".
OL,15,F"The assessment is that giving
OL,16,Fevidence without anonymity would
OL,17,Fcreate a realistic possibility that
OL,18,Fthe threat to those individuals will
OL,19,Fincrease," he said.
OL,26,@rD@QOUuD@GO]wD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FHe added: "It's on that basis that we
OL,7,Frespectfully say that the first stage
OL,8,Fof the Article Two test is satisfied
OL,9,Fon that assessment alone, if it is
OL,10,Faccepted, and we say that there is no
OL,11,Fgood reason not to accept it."
OL,13,FHe said it is "very obvious from the
OL,14,Fwealth of legacy inquest decisions
OL,15,Fthat we have and decision on others
OL,16,Foutside of the legacy inquest forum
OL,17,Fbut still within Northern Ireland that
OL,18,Ffrequently these kinds of applications
OL,19,Fare granted for former police
OL,20,Fofficers".
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@^O]uD@OOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FThe barrister clarified he was "not
OL,7,Fsuggesting the inquiry should close
OL,8,Fthe door" to rejecting anonymity
OL,9,Fapplications as there "may be other
OL,10,Fcircumstances which warrant refusal".
OL,12,FHugh Southey KC, representing some
OL,13,Fbereaved families, said they accept in
OL,14,Fprinciple the inquiry reaching
OL,15,F"generic findings" to use as a
OL,16,F"starting point essentially when
OL,17,Fassessing individual cases" but that
OL,18,Fthere still needs to be individual
OL,19,Fconsideration.
OL,26,@nD@`OUpD@IO]qD@WOUrD@dO]wD@AOUwD@RO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FHe referred to the example of the head
OL,7,Fof police saying: "For accountability
OL,8,Freasons it's obvious the Chief
OL,9,FConstable has to be a public figure
OL,10,Fand the Chief Constable gets provided
OL,11,Fwith protection and that is something
OL,12,Fthat is a proportionate response.
OL,14,F"All I am saying is that one shouldn't
OL,15,Frule out the possibility of importance
OL,16,Fbeing a factor, particularly in one
OL,17,Fsense it is a factor that may need to
OL,18,Fbe kept under review.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,F"If, for example, there was something
OL,7,Fvery serious that was said about a
OL,8,Fparticular officer it shouldn't be
OL,9,Fruled out that the fact that
OL,10,Fimportance might, in those
OL,11,Fcircumstances, justify naming the
OL,12,Findividual."
OL,14,FThe barrister also referred to the
OL,15,F"tragic killings" of PSNI Constables
OL,16,FStephen Carroll and Ronan Kerr who
OL,17,Fwere killed by dissident republican
OL,18,Fgroups, raised as an example of the
OL,19,Fthreat facing police in Northern
OL,20,FIreland by counsel for the PSNI.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784654323
OL,3,COmagh Inquiry Chair urged to keep
OL,4,C'public accountability' in mind
OL,6,FHighlighting that the terror threat
OL,7,Flevel in Northern Ireland was dropped
OL,8,Ffrom severe to substantial in 2024, Mr
OL,9,FSouthey said: "Mr Henry drew attention
OL,10,Fto the tragic killings of Constable
OL,11,FCarroll and Constable Kerr.
OL,13,F"They, of course, occurred during that
OL,14,Fpeak, and to some extent, in our
OL,15,Fsubmission, as a result, are of
OL,16,Fperhaps less significance than they
OL,17,Fmight be, because fortunately things
OL,18,Fhave improved since then, and that's
OL,19,Falso demonstrated by, as I already
OL,20,Findicated, the threat level now is
OL,21,Fsubstantial, which is a reduction."
OL,26,@qD@OOUuD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
